{"about_the_game":"<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834740/extras/ezgif-5-010081c573.gif?t=1737520076\" /><br><strong>HYPERBLADE</strong> is a gameplay-driven action game where you can only move by dashing. <br>Use your momentum to kick off walls and cut down your enemies. <br>Abilities like time manipulation and bullet deflection allow for limitless improvisational play.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834740/extras/ezgif-3-78c1a316a3.gif?t=1737520076\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Early Access</h2>HYPERBLADE has entered early access to get feedback and improve the game. The final version will expand on the story/lore, and have more levels and gameplay elements.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834740/extras/ezgif-5-5985f91411.gif?t=1737520076\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Design Pillars</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Gameplay first - HYPERBLADE prioritizes gameplay over story. No long unskippable cutscenes to interrupt the flow of gameplay.<br></li><li> Tough but fair - Players should feel challenged, but should never feel that they died unfairly.<br></li><li> A sense of mastery - A player's skill should improve over time. The satisfaction of mastering a mechanic can be extremely satisfying.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834740/extras/ezgif-5-a9a051cd18.gif?t=1737520076\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834740/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737520076","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834740/page.bg.jpg?t=1737520076","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834740/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737520076","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai